data.description: **Seller if offering 5K Concessions for Painting allowance for Full Price Offer** If you missed your chance last time...this charming home is located in Burleson ISD is back on the market and won't last long.  It has 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with new updated flooring throughout. The Living area has a woodburning fireplace for the cool chilly nights.  Private backyard with plenty of shade and privacy fencing and 2 sheds.  The Master bedroom has French-doors leading out to a back patio, and en-suite with dual sinks, a walk-in shower, 2 closets and French-doors that lead to the sunroom. The yard has a sprinkler system for watering in the hot summer months. *New roof* and foundation repair completed approximately 3 months ago!  Seller will be having home professionally cleaned upon move out!
